http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/andhra-pradesh/AR-constable-commits-suicide/article14015593.ece

A head constable of Guntur Urban Armed Reserve force B. Venkata Reddy on Friday committed suicide on the premises of the Police Parade Grounds by consuming poison.Mr. Reddy, 55, a native of Mangalagiri, reportedly separated from his wife and had been in a state of depression since then, sources said.The AR police gathered on the grounds for an annual mobilisation programme in which they would be trained in the use of weapons and in controlling law and order.Sources said that Mr. Reddy had come to the grounds after consuming poison.The personnel who saw him collapsing rushed him to a private hospital where he died.